The paper deals with the problem of face alignment using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of large datasets and the training of neural networks, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the creation of a new dataset, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR).
